description: This header file declares exported API functions related to the 'Slap Dslh ParamTree' component, including creation, removal, object mapping, and descriptor functions for the SLAP environment.

methods.name: SlapCreateDslhParamTree
methods.description: Creates a new Dslh ParamTree object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: SlapDslhParamtoGetSlapObjCallMap
methods.description: Retrieves the call map for the Slap DslhParamto object.

methods.name: SlapDslhParamtoGetSlapObjDescriptor
methods.description: Retrieves the object descriptor for the Slap DslhParamto object.

methods.name: SlapDslhParamtoCreate
methods.description: Instantiates a new Slap DslhParamto object with specified contexts.

methods.name: SlapDslhParamtoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the specified Slap DslhParamto object.

methods.name: SlapDslhParamtoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Slap DslhParamto object.
